</td></tr><tr><td>&#x02003;&#x02022; Impaired glucose tolerance (ICD-9 790.22 or ICD-10 R73.02)</td><td>&#x02022; Cirrhosis (ICD-9 571 or ICD-10&#x000a0;K74.60)<sup>a</sup>
